  "description": "This beautiful 6-bedroom Family Villa offers bright and spacious accommodation, fabulous outdoor space and has an idyllic location in Guadalmina Baja, just a short walk to the beach and all amenities.\n\nCasa Del Mar offers many luxurious features and has abundant outdoor space both around the pool and the purpose-built BBQ area, as well as the large lawn for young children. The pool is gated, providing an extra safeguard for young children and has the option to be heated (at an additional weekly charge). The garden and pool areas, together with the BBQ/Bar area make for easy and comfortable outdoor living and dining.\n\nThe villa is bright and spacious with a good distribution and an easy flow.  All the bedrooms are of a good size, with ample wardrobe space, hot/cold aircon as well as ceiling fans for the summer months and dedicated heating for the winter months, ensuring everyone will be more than comfortable.\n\nThe ground floor consists of the large and well-equipped kitchen, with easy access to the dining and living areas.  Also, on the ground floor are 3 en-suite bedrooms as well as a guest WC.\n\nOn the upper floor are 3 more bedrooms, one of which is en-suite and the other two share a full bathroom.\n\nAdditional features include Table Tennis, satellite TV, WiFi, electric gates and an alarm system. Furthermore, regular housekeeping is included twice a week!\n\nCasa Del Mar is just a 450m walk from long stretch of sandy beach offering a magnificent area for swimming, just west of the well-known Puerto Banús. The beach-side neighbourhood is very well maintained and the streets going down to the beach are safe to walk.\n\nPlease note that we welcome families and couples only, no groups under 30, and no hen or stag parties. Should you fall outside of this category but wish to book nonetheless, please send us an enquiry detailing a bit more about yourself and the group that you will be travelling with so we can request this for you.",
